{"tid":2016814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"American Sniper 與香港手足","createTime":"2020-05-14T16:23:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T13:35:07.000Z","uid":245711,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"36a3164150b8f3ccf2ddaa076fe07a83c1a0a4d2","tid":2016814,"uid":245711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T16:23:32.000Z","msg":"香港: 多名勇武手足出現「精神創傷」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2016569\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2016569</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n最近睇咗套戲叫American Sniper，每一幕雖然都喺美國或者中東，但愈睇愈覺得係連繫住香港每個手足嘅故事，於是有幾點想同大家分享。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x5UmrkA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx5UmrkA.jpg&h=60fb391b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U5tKo7k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU5tKo7k.jpg&h=d958253f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. [愛香港]</span> </span>選擇上前線嘅手足可以有種種背景，但歸因到底都係出於愛香港。Chris睇到新聞報道入面自己國家嘅大使館被炸，死傷慘重而報考US Navy；我哋每一個又未曾試過睇直播見到白衫人恐襲、催淚彈橫飛感到憤慨而踏出多一步？<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6TqAvNv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6TqAvNv.jpg&h=e08858d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2. [愛自己]</span></span> 戰場上能力愈大責任愈大，但記住戰爭將會係漫長，甚至係永無休止嘅。目睹同伴被重創被殺，Chris將呢啲悲憤轉為動力，一次又一次再上戰場最後仲英雄式咁射殺咗對方皇牌，但然後呢？戰場上生存得到嘅悔疚感令佢返到美國時候跟本唔能夠正常生活，聽到引擎聲都會諗起機槍聲。呢點相信香港手足都身同感受，見到紅藍燈自然諗起有狗車出沒，甚或者有紙包飲品爆開都聯想到TG，長期嚟講絕對係唔健康。就好似Chris最後轉去退伍軍人福利做分享一樣，要貢獻香港亦唔只得街頭抗爭一條路。有時候將自己所見所想、政治願景分享出嚟，唔單止係文宣一種，亦係自己下一次上場前一個好好嘅準備。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EekQjF1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEekQjF1.jpg&h=41a2333c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3. [靜靜雞]</span></span> 愈出名嘅人就愈危險，因為你在明而對家在暗。當Chris放低咗之前參與戰爭嘅陰霾，重新同家人建立關係享受天倫之樂之際，就被一個聲稱有求於佢嘅前士兵殺死。佢喺中東槍林彈雨都留得住自己性命，最後都係喪命喺自己得州同鄉手上。同理，手足喺街頭上可能球技了得入好多波，但身邊嘅隨時係人係鬼都唔知。對家人手同Cam咁充足嘅情況下有咩戰績都係留返煲底先講好啲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/svoa37L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsvoa37L.jpg&h=a59b781c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後希望大家記住，作為命運共同體，對自己好就係對大家好；收放自如，文武有時正正就係Be Water嘅精粹所在。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(圖: @rthk @humchuk)"},{"pid":"77ae3569bab2a27307ab1df9fd118724436bde55","tid":2016814,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T16:25:57.000Z","msg":"<em></em>"},{"pid":"b38f79e9767221038fe1e50cc3e2fce7ab854abe","tid":2016814,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T16:26:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a074f67c82c23d22cad20362490d908249de0cc3","tid":2016814,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T16:27:07.000Z","msg":"內容Ok<br />\n但標題唔太吸引"},{"pid":"e4a8c8e047e7637011d7a312a5210c1e1127083c","tid":2016814,"uid":11423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T16:28:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3313d1e7f9c20293a2920fc6049a5e30bd6db634","tid":2016814,"uid":245711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a074f67c82c23d22cad20362490d908249de0cc3","tid":2016814,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T16:27:07.000Z","msg":"內容Ok<br />\n但標題唔太吸引"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T16:31:55.000Z","msg":"Thanks for 推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔識定標題 應該要做標題黨？<br />\n「美國狙擊手同香港手足都有關係？！？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d28cbf9c87701e3e2261264e7f7b49bc238cfd","tid":2016814,"uid":83865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T16:35:24.000Z","msg":"明你講咩"},{"pid":"dbca0ef84a047b21071827e0cfe04ea48bdb9678","tid":2016814,"uid":245711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14